  "3188560": {
    "name": "Empty Skull Demo",
    "steam_appid": 3188560,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188560/extras/ec8695e1d9b5434be54011110df371bb.poster.avif?t=1755171560\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188560/extras/ec8695e1d9b5434be54011110df371bb.webm?t=1755171560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188560/extras/ec8695e1d9b5434be54011110df371bb.mp4?t=1755171560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>“有时候，想要记起你曾是谁，就必须穿越那些从未存在过的世界。”</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>你醒来了。四周一片虚无。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>你不知道你是谁。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>你感觉不到疼痛。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>你感觉不到身体。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>你只是一颗骷髅头。像你的心一样空洞。哦对了，你没有心。哟呵呵呵呵呵。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188560/extras/e9e485ddc4d340fa77a6aa0fe0f7b919.poster.avif?t=1755171560\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188560/extras/e9e485ddc4d340fa77a6aa0fe0f7b919.webm?t=1755171560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188560/extras/e9e485ddc4d340fa77a6aa0fe0f7b919.mp4?t=1755171560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Empty Skull（空之骷髅）</u></strong> 是一款氛围感十足的冒险解谜游戏，在游戏中你将探索神秘的维度、诡异的生物、失落的记忆碎片……还有那些，也许只存在于你脑海中的声音。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当你越来越深入这些世界之间的世界时，你会逐渐意识到：你来这里并非偶然。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188560/extras/3371a79f5d7b0a0515dfd6cfbed283a5.poster.avif?t=1755171560\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188560/extras/3371a79f5d7b0a0515dfd6cfbed283a5.webm?t=1755171560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188560/extras/3371a79f5d7b0a0515dfd6cfbed283a5.mp4?t=1755171560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一扇门、每一个问题、每一次低语——都是你的一部分。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但你真的想要记起真相吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>游戏特色：</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大量谜题，考验你的逻辑、观察力与想象力。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >引人入胜的剧情，充满意想不到的转折——通过细节讲述，没有冗长的过场动画，每个世界元素都隐藏着深意。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >各不相同的维度世界：从3D世界中无法说话的骷髅，到2D世界里完全寂静的空间；从一切已经发生的地方，到一切尚未开始的未来。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >奇特的角色：有的会帮助你，有的会考验你，还有的会问出你最害怕面对的问题。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >音效设计贴合你的情绪变化，为你的旅程增添氛围。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188560/extras/63836d625ea0abbe29be35824b5dc977.poster.avif?t=1755171560\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188560/extras/63836d625ea0abbe29be35824b5dc977.webm?t=1755171560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188560/extras/63836d625ea0abbe29be35824b5dc977.mp4?t=1755171560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>适合谁来玩这款游戏？</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>适合喜欢以下内容的玩家：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >氛围浓厚、剧情出人意料的故事；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >谜题挑战；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过环境探索剧情。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>而在游戏最后，你将面对一个抉择——它将决定你的命运。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188560/extras/bb68c29da9e0f0653948af0ef8e166e3.poster.avif?t=1755171560\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188560/extras/bb68c29da9e0f0653948af0ef8e166e3.webm?t=1755171560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188560/extras/bb68c29da9e0f0653948af0ef8e166e3.mp4?t=1755171560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>你愿意穿越多少个维度，才能找到答案——</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>为什么你会变成一颗空洞的骷髅？</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>还有……你曾经，真的存在过吗？</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188560/extras/a5e2030666211c2869abbbe1fee102f7.poster.avif?t=1755171560\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188560/extras/a5e2030666211c2869abbbe1fee102f7.webm?t=1755171560\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188560/extras/a5e2030666211c2869abbbe1fee102f7.mp4?t=1755171560\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
